Perfect thanks! I filtered them and organize by blocks: [https://bitbucket.org/snippets/\_jrivero\_/9egE87](https://bitbucket.org/snippets/_jrivero_/9egE87)

If I have to bet I would put some money to the mix of dart packages versions or to the fact that we’ve introduced changes that make the code slow during the new prereleases. In the first case, we can add a bit more of metadata to force the migration to 6.9 for all dart packages. In the second case, I think that is out of the scope of this PR.
